      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that but i have so much work to do this week and its super expensive to get an xray and everything. it doesnt even look deformed or anything, just really puffy. i'm pretty sure it's just a bad sprain. isnt rice literally the standard thing for this? if i just keep it elevated and take some ibuprofen for a few days i should be okay right? it'll probably feel better by tomorrow.",
